title: Hollywood Lashes Out at Trump for Calls to ‘Liberate’ MI, MN, VA : 'He Is Going to Get More People Killed'
description: Left-wing Hollywood stars are melting down over President Donald Trump's calls to "liberate" three Democrat-led states where residents have risen up in protest, demanding that governors re-open the economies and relax restrictions on physical movement.
